iZiving — Private Zcash fundraising (like giving, with a z).	
iAgent/MCP discovery card (Gopher-over-HTTPS). Type 1 = drill in, 0 = read, h = follow URL.	
iNo custody, no KYC: donors pay the fundraiser's shielded wallet directly.	
